{
  "stem": "12029.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she was somewhere else, because there she could hide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She couldn't hide in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I went there, I said goodbye to Grandma.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I left, going back to our apartment, I saw Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Janusz Korczak walking with the children to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was a scene that I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had four children in his hands-- two in each hand and two under the arms-- six children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the rest follow him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can tell you forever I remind myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Today, it breaks my  heart how this Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Korczak [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went with those children to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We still didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few days later, my mother-- no that was before-- my mother and my auntie were called and taken to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we somehow knew a policeman who could bring them back for money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the morning, they were coming back, and we went to meet them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I passed by, on the street to go there, and the streets were full of dead bodies, because if they didn't catch you, and they saw you in the distance, they shot.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know, I didn't tell you exactly even from before how there was a German who we called Frankenstein.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He never had a cup of coffee till he killed five Jews every morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You see, you can't realize how hard was the life in the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] uncle worked in the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] also in that factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day, those directors from the factory wanted to make a concert.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they made them take a piano from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
